00:02:19.840 --> 00:02:20.340
Aah!

00:02:20.340 --> 00:02:21.780
I get to write on "Ema" too! [3]

00:02:22.160 --> 00:02:24.280
Awesome! Let's go write one!

00:02:25.580 --> 00:02:27.280
The category of my ema..

00:02:27.280 --> 00:02:28.380
"Relationship Fortune"

00:02:28.680 --> 00:02:30.840
And for the wish content...

00:02:31.060 --> 00:02:31.560
Okay!

00:02:32.200 --> 00:02:33.760
"Get to meet a lot of people

00:02:33.760 --> 00:02:34.960
and be friendly with them!"

00:02:35.160 --> 00:02:38.000
