00:02:53.860 --> 00:02:56.600
I'm going to put one up in my website so 
please come and visit later, okay?

00:02:56.880 --> 00:02:57.540
Alright!

00:02:57.540 --> 00:02:59.600
We've done our first hatsumōde! Yay!

00:02:59.600 --> 00:03:01.000
With this, 2017 will be

00:03:01.000 --> 00:03:02.720
awesome, don't you think?

